fields.name: Description
fields.value:
Hands in the air, onii-chan!

You're going to jail for lewding lolis and not being in the Lolice Discord server!

Join today and take part in securing the safety of our flat friends! The Official Lolice Discord community serves as a great place to chat with lovely people or make new friends. The force is led by none other than Lolice Chief Confessor! Please contact him for any questions you may have.

Can you say 10-15 years, onii-chan?
